    h1 Vital's Versatility
    hr
    p Vital is a fresh alternative to heavily structured frameworks that require deep nesting and excessive markup. Vital is hyper-minimal by design, the advantages you gain in this framework are:
    ul
      li Lightweight (~10KB compressed)
      li Quick and easy to learn
      li Fairly style agnostic and easy to customize
      li Easy to read, write and maintain
    h2 Modify or Override
    p One-size does not fit all. Vital is built on the principal of flexibility. Vital can be directly modified (or overridden if you prefer), thus allowing your application styles to mature into specific application styles.
